  "summary": "Malicious code in type-async (npm)",
  "details": "Type-async@3.3.7 is a trojanized package impersonating a logging library. When required, it spawns a detached child process that fetches a payload from hxxps://json[.]extendsclass[.]com/bin/250fca079abb and executes it via the Function constructor, enabling arbitrary remote code execution. The package also contains base64-encoded references to a second pastebin endpoint (jsonkeeper[.]com/b/XRGF3). The package description is unrelated to its name, and it has no repository or verifiable provenance.",
